import React, { useReducer, useContext } from 'react';
import { StyleSheet, View, Button } from 'react-native';
import LevelFirst from '../../levels/LevelFirst'
import LevelSecond from '../../levels/LevelSecond'
import LevelThird from '../../levels/LevelThird'
import LevelFourth from '../../levels/LevelFourth'
import LevelFifth from '../../levels/LevelFifth'
import LevelSixth from '../../levels/LevelSixth'
import LevelSeventh from '../../levels/LevelSeventh'
import LevelEight from '../../levels/LevelEight'
import LevelNinth from '../../levels/LevelNinth'
import LevelTenth from '../../levels/LevelTenth'

export const CountContext = React.createContext()

const initialState = <Game />;

const reducer = (state, action) => {
    switch (action) {
        case '1':
            return <LevelFirst />
        case '2':
            return <LevelSecond />
        case '3':
            return <LevelThird />
        case '4':
            return <LevelFourth />
        case '5':
            return <LevelFifth />
        case '6':
            return <LevelSixth />
        case '7':
            return <LevelSeventh />
        case '8':
            return <LevelEight />
        case '9':
            return <LevelNinth />
        case '10':
            return <LevelTenth />
        default:
            return state
    }
}

export const Game = () => {
    const [count, dispatch] = useReducer(reducer, initialState)
    const countContext = useContext(CountContext)

    return <>
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('1')} title='Level 1' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('2')} title='Level 2' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('3')} title='Level 3' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('4')} title='Level 4' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('5')} title='Level 5' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('6')} title='Level 6' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('7')} title='Level 7' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('8')} title='Level 8' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('9')} title='Level 9' />
        <Button onPress={() => dispatch('10')} title='Level 10' />
    </>
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
});
